  <br>
  Actually I was anything but bored. Especially after dropping down into a pit and finding myself alone with an Efretti, a couple elementals and a goblin wizard to keep me company. <br>
<br>
  It would be preference to keep raids to one level range at a time until we have become a bit more successful at running these. Keep to a single location for a month but have different raids based on level range. As Mystic did by setting a level range for their raid. However, I will support and stand by any decision the guild makes. <br>
<br>
Arichiena <br>
